channel.title: Model help
channel.description: Ok, so I'm new to models and client stuff so i recolored a godsword and made it with datmaker and made it a dat. After that i made it a rar file and added it to models then i configured the java files and made the ID 16099 after that i went on my server and said Add model 1113 since the model was 1113 and the drop model was 1114 so i said Add model 1114 but it nothing happened... i need help because when i spawn it, it comes out as a tile lol... well is there any other way to do this? Please help me..
